org.jboss.windup.tooling

Interface ExecutionResults

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecutionResultsImpl

    public interface ExecutionResults
extends Serializable
    Contains the results of running Windup. This contains all Classifications, Hints, and information about how to find the reports that were produced.
    Author:
    Jesse Sightler, Ondrej Zizka

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      List<ReportLink> getReportLinks()
      Contains information about all of the reports produced by Windup and how to find them.
      String getWindupStopOnRequestMessage()
      A message about Windup stopping on request before finishing, if that happened; null otherwise.
